{"tw": {"3845630": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "調教按摩店 ～瑪麗篇～", "steam_appid": 3845630, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.poster.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.webm?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.mp4?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/55c00f9c99ab7a52d87a601f735b2ded.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >瑪麗是一個安靜又焦慮的女孩，原本只是想找限量史萊姆周邊，卻陰錯陽差來到一間小型身心療癒中心。櫃台接待員黛娜雖然有點古怪，卻十分親切，建議她嘗試一次舒壓療程。瑪麗雖然猶豫，卻因好奇而答應了。接下來，就看你能否讓她真正放鬆，感受到輕盈自在。她會因你的觸感得到慰藉，還是被嚇得退縮？找到她最需要安撫的部位，也許她會再度回來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/db35b8db17f3a1a723ff3708fccfc1cf.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你將扮演一位按摩理療師，幫助瑪麗舒緩壓力，重建自信。透過合宜的觸碰、揉壓與牽引，讓她在關鍵時刻感受到安心與愉悅。你的雙手將探索她身體的每一個部位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >放鬆她的緊繃，贏得她的信任……或許，她會完全向你敞開，帶來難以忘懷的體驗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/786b57b6a1039efdcbc27d438d0d5cd6.poster.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/786b57b6a1039efdcbc27d438d0d5cd6.webm?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/9c9d31c22681f18b0b06665fea368060.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>動態場景</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作呈現流暢自然的動畫效果，每一次按摩互動都清晰展現。無論是輕撫、揉壓或點按，動作都生動細膩。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>觸感交流</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作為理療師，你需要以雙手細緻地為瑪麗進行按摩。當技巧純熟並贏得她的信任後，將可解鎖更多互動方式。放慢腳步，你一定能掌握。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>情緒管理</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨時關注她的心情，確保她對療程感到滿意。若在不適當的時機開口，或在她尚未準備好時過度親近，她就不會再回來。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>關係發展與多重結局</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著療程推進，你將逐步揭開更多關於你與瑪麗的故事。遊戲中的抉擇將決定你迎來的結局。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.poster.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.webm?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5c