雲端"}, {"id": 62, "description": "親友同享"}], "genres": [{"id": "28", "description": "模擬"}], "release_date": {"coming_soon": false, "date": "2025 年 12 月 5 日"}}}}, "us": {"3845630": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "The Taming Massage Parlor ~Mari's Story~", "steam_appid": 3845630, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.poster.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.webm?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.mp4?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/07af18d2b47317c623cd0bccf66130f1.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mari, a quiet and anxious girl, sets out to find some limited-edition slime merchandise but ends up at a small wellness center by mistake. The receptionist, Dana, is a bit unusual but kind, and suggests Mari try a stress-relief session instead. Unsure but curious, Mari agrees. Now it's up to you to help her relax and feel a little lighter. Will she find some relief through your touch or will you scare her away? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the right spots on her body, and you might just see her return.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/1ce7a3f2af781d420dcec12995776754.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of a massage therapist helping Mari manage stress and rebuild her confidence. Touch, rub, and pull the right spots at the right time for her pleasure. Let your hands explore every part of her body. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ease her tension, gain her trust... and she might open herself completely, in ways you won’t forget.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/11548d9e68d07a4bd76abd1c3e8201b4.poster.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/11548d9e68d07a4bd76abd1c3e8201b4.webm?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/90d409ac5aa8dc93dc04895e86ba6502.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Animated Scenes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game offers smooth and natural animations of every interaction durring each massage session. Every touch, rub and poke is animated!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Touchy Feely</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a masseur, it's your job to rub your hands all over Mari's body.  If you're confident with your techniques and gained enough of her trust, you can even try to use more than your hands! Raising her self-esteem unlocks more interactions. Just take it slow and you'll do fine.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mood Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay attention to her mood and make sure she's happy with your service. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speak at the wrong moment, or move into more intimate touch before she’s ready, and she won’t be back for another session!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deeper Relationship and Multiple Endings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through each session, you can unlock more of the story between you and Mari. The choices you make throughout the game will determine which ending you get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.poster.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=202 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.webm?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/68fd877c5cf0047d5a136e5217583104.mp4?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/07af18d2b47317c623cd0bccf66130f1.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mari, a quiet and anxious girl, sets out to find some limited-edition slime merchandise but ends up at a small wellness center by mistake. The receptionist, Dana, is a bit unusual but kind, and suggests Mari try a stress-relief session instead. Unsure but curious, Mari agrees. Now it's up to you to help her relax and feel a little lighter. Will she find some relief through your touch or will you scare her away? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find the right spots on her body, and you might just see her return.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/1ce7a3f2af781d420dcec12995776754.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of a massage therapist helping Mari manage stress and rebuild her confidence. Touch, rub, and pull the right spots at the right time for her pleasure. Let your hands explore every part of her body. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Ease her tension, gain her trust... and she might open herself completely, in ways you won’t forget.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/11548d9e68d07a4bd76abd1c3e8201b4.poster.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=488 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/11548d9e68d07a4bd76abd1c3e8201b4.webm?t=1764989968\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/extras/90d409ac5aa8dc93dc04895e86ba6502.avif?t=1764989968\" width=616 height=124 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Animated Scenes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game offers smooth and natural animations of every interaction durring each massage session. Every touch, rub and poke is animated!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Touchy Feely</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As a masseur, it's your job to rub your hands all over Mari's body.  If you're confident with your techniques and gained enough of her trust, you can even try to use more than your hands! Raising her self-esteem unlocks more interactions. Just take it slow and you'll do fine.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Mood Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pay attention to her mood and make sure she's happy with your service. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Speak at the wrong moment, or move into more intimate touch before she’s ready, and she won’t be back for another session!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Deeper Relationship and Multiple Endings</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you progress through each session, you can unlock more of the story between you and Mari. The choices you make throughout the game will determine which ending you get.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "short_description": "Mari stumbles into a wellness center by mistake and ends up trying a stress-relief session. As her therapist, guide her through gentle conversation and intimate touch. Ease her tension, earn her trust, and help her feel more confident with her body, one session at a time.", "supported_languages": "English, Japanese<strong>*</strong>, Korean, Simplified Chinese, Traditional Chinese<br><strong>*</strong>languages with full audio support", "header_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/25582df2deca9c93a74130df50e2511fa8700286/header.jpg?t=1764989968", "capsule_image": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/c5494c422b7bc6ed8e46bf5910eaf4315488eb80/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1764989968", "capsule_imagev5": "https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3845630/c5494c422b7bc6ed8e46bf5910eaf4315488eb80/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1764989968", "website": "https://saikeystu